sentences: Nayer Nagui (born 1970) is an Egyptian composer, conductor, musical director and pianist.
Nagui was born in Alexandria in 1970.

Nayer is a conductor at Cairo Opera House, recently the Chief Conductor of Cairo Conservatory Orchestras.
Since 2004, he has been  sharing the baton with the French Conductor Michel Piquemal, in conducting the “Coro de Tres Culturas” in the Moroccan "Festival de printemps des Alizes".
